title: Root System

creator: Edrean Ernst
descriptionHtml:
This is the mobile companion app for the Allesbeste Root System, which was developed by farmers for farmers.

This app will make it a lot easier to do your day-to-day in-field data capturing, such as:
- Soil moisture scouting
- Scouting for weeds
- Estimating your harvest in-field
- Daily timesheet clocking of personnel
- Connecting with the Allesbeste scales to do harvesting transactions
- Monitoring your harvesting process in real-time

...and more to come.

To use this app you will need your account credentials from the Root System which can be obtained by visiting the service's website (https://app.rootsolutions.tech) and signing up for a free account.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Only cosmetic improvements to some graphics.

title: Root System
